the handler to me.

536
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:38,750
And as for the intrepid agent…

537
00:29:38,818 --> 00:29:41,420
Tell Topher to prep Echo.

538
00:29:43,322 --> 00:29:46,592
I think they're ready
for a second date.

539
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:55,157
Hey, everyone's got
their fantasies, right?

540
00:29:55,197 --> 00:29:56,960
A guy wants to know
what it's like,

541
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:59,178
you know, to be
with another man.

542
00:29:59,201 --> 00:30:01,002
just once,
nothing queeny.

543
00:30:10,379 --> 00:30:11,699
(chuckles awkwardly)

544
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,361
Oh-ho.

545
00:30:26,428 --> 00:30:27,996
You're bad.

546
00:30:28,062 --> 00:30:30,230
