I can handle that?

578
00:32:31,354 --> 00:32:34,483
Uh, not everything
is about you, infinite ego man.

579
00:32:34,523 --> 00:32:36,185
You know, you did
nail the guy

580
00:32:36,225 --> 00:32:37,386
