00:39:17,617 --> 00:39:19,852
(grunting)

697
00:39:25,059 --> 00:39:26,926
(groans)

698
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,768
(groans)

699
00:39:36,637 --> 00:39:38,539
(pots clanging)

700
00:39:43,344 --> 00:39:45,111
(groans)

701
00:39:50,852 --> 00:39:52,953
(bowls and plates crashing)

702
00:39:55,422 --> 00:39:57,357
(grunting)
(groans)

703
00:39:59,359 --> 00:40:00,627
(groans)

704
00:40:16,143 --> 00:40:17,529
(grunting)
(groaning)

705
00:40:23,918 --> 00:40:26,320
(groans)

706
00:40:29,090 --> 00:40:30,156
(groans)

707
00:40:43,637 --> 00:40:45,238
(groans)

708
00:40:47,641 --> 00:40:49,176
(panting)

709
00:40:49,242 --> 00:40:51,211
The Dollhouse is real.

710
00:40:51,277 --> 00:40:52,507
They know you're
after them

711
00:40:52,547 --> 00:40:53,907
and they are going
to have you taken

712
00:40:53,947 --> 00:40:55,644
off the case.
That's why they sent me.

713
00:40:55,684 --> 00:40:57,684
(panting)

714
00:40:58,918 --> 00:41:00,887
Why are you
telling me this?

715
00:41:10,996 --> 00:41:12,993
This is their first
communication.

716
00:41:13,033 --> 00:41:16,000
Security inside
is very tight.

717
00:41:16,070 --> 00:41:18,004
Where is it?

718
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:20,305
You can't know that.

719
00:41:20,375 --> 00:41:22,335
You're going about this
the wrong way.

720
00:41:22,375 --> 00:41:23,870
I have to take down
the Dollhouse.

721
00:41:23,910 --> 00:41:25,472
There are over 20 Dollhouses,

722
00:41:25,512 --> 00:41:27,379
in cities around
the world.

723
00:41:27,449 --> 00:41:28,476
They have ties
to every

724
00:41:28,516 --> 00:41:30,511
major political power
on the planet.

725
00:41:30,551 --> 00:41:32,546
You cannot possibly
stop them alone.

726
00:41:32,586 --> 00:41:34,387
You're going to help me?

727
00:41:34,455 --> 00:41:36,897
The person that
sent this message is.

728
00:41:36,957 --> 00:41:38,559
Why?

729
00:41:38,625 --> 00:41:39,592
The Dollhouse

730
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:40,782
Deals in fantasy.

731
00:41:40,828 --> 00:41:42,054
That is their business,

732
00:41:42,094 --> 00:41:43,925
but that is not their purpose.

733
00:41:43,965 --> 00:41:45,430
What is?

734
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:47,434
We need you to find out.

735
00:41:47,500 --> 00:41:48,663
We'll contact
you again—

736
00:41:48,703 --> 00:41:51,137
if possible,
with this same body.

737
00:41:51,203 --> 00:41:53,740
But you have to let
the Dollhouse win.

738
00:41:53,807 --> 00:41:55,875
Make them back off.

739
00:41:55,941 --> 00:41:58,844
You have to trust me.

740
00:41:59,879 --> 00:42:01,814
(footfalls)
he's got

741
00:42:11,057 --> 00:42:12,324
No.
You have to go.

742
00:42:12,393 --> 00:42:13,760
They don't want

743
