protect the information.

744
00:42:16,896 --> 00:42:17,624
Call an ambulance!

745
00:42:17,664 --> 00:42:19,266
Officer down!
Go!

746
00:42:19,332 --> 00:42:20,761
You can't just….
They will protect

747
00:42:20,801 --> 00:42:22,268
the information.

748
00:42:22,336 --> 00:42:23,331
They don't want
you dead.

749
00:42:23,371 --> 00:42:24,493
But anyone else….

750
00:42:24,539 --> 00:42:26,205
Mellie.

751
00:42:28,742 --> 00:42:30,742
