771
00:44:38,885 --> 00:44:41,320
Everyone you love, strangers.

772
00:44:41,387 --> 00:44:42,555
Maybe enemies.

773
00:44:42,623 --> 00:44:45,557
Every part of you
that makes you more

774
00:44:45,625 --> 00:44:49,229
than a walking cluster
of neurons

775
00:44:49,295 --> 00:44:52,230
dissolved
at someone else's whim.

776
00:44:52,297 --> 00:44:55,066
If that technology exists—

777
00:44:55,135 --> 00:44:56,234
It'll be used.

778
00:44:56,301 --> 00:44:58,238
It'll be abused.

779
00:44:58,305 --> 00:45:00,238
It'll be global.

780
00:45:44,785 --> 00:45:46,112
Dominic: I understand.
Thank you.

781
00:45:46,152 --> 00:45:47,887
We'll talk soon.

782
00:45:47,953 --> 00:45:50,917
Agent Paul Ballard was
suspended of duty pending

783
00:45:50,957 --> 00:45:53,419
an investigation into the
shooting of Officer Hardin.

784
00:45:53,459 --> 00:45:56,428
Accusations of violent
paranoia, the attack

785
00:45:56,496 --> 00:45:57,792
on Mr Mynor's bodyguards,

786
00:45:57,832 --> 00:45:59,526
the feud with
the Borodins,

787
00:45:59,566 --> 00:46:02,602
as evidenced by the break-in
at his apartment.

788
00:46:11,012 --> 00:46:12,611
I replayed the tap.

789
00:46:12,680 --> 00:46:14,113
More than once?

790
00:46:14,180 --> 00:46:15,476
It did not lack
for poetry.

791
00:46:15,516 --> 00:46:18,449
Bring her in so Topher
can run a diagnostic.

792
00:46:18,518 --> 00:46:20,453
Are we pulling her?

793
00:46:20,520 --> 00:46:22,481
Now that Ballard's
off the case?

794
00:46:22,521 --> 00:46:23,749
No. A man like Ballard

795
00:46:23,789 --> 00:46:25,185
doesn't take himself
out of the game,

796
00:46:25,225 --> 00:46:26,658
just because of this.

797
00:46:26,727 --> 00:46:28,660
Besides…

798
00:46:28,729 --> 00:46:30,662
She loves him.

799
00:46:30,730 --> 00:46:32,292
You played
a good hand, ma'am.

800
00:46:32,332 --> 00:46:33,960
I played a very bad
hand very well.

801
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:35,128
There is a distinction.

802
